 road network nodes from the nearest bus of the distribution
 network, traf c intensity and grid stability are considered
 as key factors for nding the candidate sites for placing the
 charging stations. The potential of Bayesian network to deal
 with uncertainty and interaction among different events is
 used in the present work TheBayesian networkutilized in the
 present work to ndthecandidate locations for the placement
 of charging stations is as shown in Fig.1.
