tance. The states of Congestion are {Low, High}, states
 of VSF are {Low, Medium, High}, states of Distance are
 {Low, Medium, High} and the states of the child node Can
didate are {Yes, No}. The probability that a particular node
 is a candidate location is computed by bucket elimination
 algorithm [14] [17] as given by Eq. (1).
