 computed by bucket elimination algorithm [13] [17]. The
 states of the root nodes Day, Time, and Area are
 {Weekday, Weekend},{AM Peak, Work, PM Peak, Leisure,
 Rest}, {Residential(R), Of ce (O), Market (M), School (Sc)}
 respectively. The states of the child node Traf c ow are
 {Low (L), Medium (M), High (H)}. The states of the node
