Another objective of DFCM is to minimize the queuing
time of EVs at the charging station. An EV immediately starts
charging on arrival at the charging station if a charging point
is available. If all points are occupied, then EV has to wait
until a point becomes available. Hence, the charging strategy
adopted is based on first-come-first-serve. Thus, the objective
is to minimize the average time an EV waits in a queue for a
charging point to become available, which is
