 D. EFFECTOFCHARGINGSTATIONPLACEMENT
 ONDISTRIBUTIONNETWORK
 Thechargingstationsaffect theoperatingparametersofthe
 distributionnetworksuchasvoltagedeviation,reliability,and
 power loss.However, thevoltagepro lesof all thebuses
 (Fig. 7)werewithinacceptable limit for all the sixplans
 reported inTable8. Fig. 8, Fig. 9andFig. 10 showthe
 impactofchargingstationplacementonthe threereliabil
ity indicesnamedSAIFI,SAIDI, andCAIDI respectively.
