{Learner Phase}
Choose two learners Zi and Zj, i̸= j;
if(ﬁtness of Zi better than Zj)
Replace ith learner by Znew = Zold + rand × (Zi −Zj); %
rand is a random number
Else
Replace ith learner by Znew = Zold + rand × (Zj −Zi);
